data.title: Birthplace of Paul Dresser, Terre Haute, IN
data.meta_description:
Paul Dresser (1859-1906) composed ON THE BANKS OF THE WABASH, Indiana's State Song...moved in 1963 from 318 So. 2nd to Fairbanks Park, 1st and Farring, on Dresser Drive.
	Color photo by Mitchell
